# Navbar (Header) rules

## Must
- Use MUI `AppBar` + `Toolbar` with three zones:
  - Logo (Hebrew brand name)
  - Navigation links
  - Actions (outlined login, contained signup)
- Action buttons must be pill-shaped (`borderRadius: '999px'`).
- All labels must be Hebrew only.
- Use `react-router-dom` navigation (`Link`/`RouterLink`), not raw anchors.

## Never
- Do not hardcode colors in CSS for light-only. If styling is needed, rely on theme (`sx`) so dark mode works.
- Do not use emojis in nav labels.

